  "title": "Slash Length",
  "description": "A simple mod that removes the chat limit when typing commands",
  "body": "<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <center>\n<img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1s0LP2Gc7tyDH65WZX_dC9TPYTOzYlIwZ\"  alt=\"Beam Be Gone Logo\">\n<h2>\n<b>A simple mod that removes the chat limit when typing commands</b>\n</h2>\n  <P>(there is no command added. /Length is just the name)</P>\n<br>\n<a href=\"\">\n<img alt=\"modrinth\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/modrinth_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/RamGemes/SlashLength\">\n<img alt=\"github\" height=\"56\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/cozy/available/github_vector.svg\">\n</a>\n<br>\n<img alt=\"fabric\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/supported/fabric_vector.svg\">\n<img alt=\"forge\" height=\"40\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@intergrav/devins-badges@3/assets/compact/unsupported/forge_vector.svg\">\n</center>\n</div>\n\n## Note on Java Version\nYou will need to use JAVA 21 in order to use this mod. If you are stuck on JAVA 17, you can install a newer version of JAVA here: [(link to Adoptium's JDKs)](https://adoptium.net/temurin/releases/)\n\n## License\n\n---\nThis project is under an MIT license",
